[li](3) [a href="http://www.deloitte.com/assets/Dcom-UnitedStates/Local%20Assets/Documents/Health%20Reform%20Issues%20Briefs/US_CHS_ComparativeEffectivenessResearchintheUS_062711.pdf"]Deloitte - Issue Brief Comparative Effectiveness Research in the United States: Update and implications (PDF)[/a][/li]
